'''Chav''' was a sweet drink used to make [[Glowblue Noodles and Chav]].

During the time Luke Skywalker was accompanied by [[Darial Anglethorn]] on the planet [[Beheboth]], Darial offered Skywalker a mug of hot chav.<ref name="Star Wars 66">[[Star Wars (1977) 66|''Star Wars'' (1977) 66]]</ref>

